Package: scrnaseq.cellcomm
Title: scrnaseq-cellcomm: package containing all functions used in the GaitiLab/scrnaseq-cellcomm-pipeline
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Joan", "Kant", email = "Joan.Kant@uhn.ca", role = c("cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-1837-5854"))
Description: scrnaseq-cellcomm comprises of all functions used in the GaitiLab/scrnaseq-cellcomm-pipeline which aims to infer cell-cell-interactions from scRNAseq data. This is done by leveraging publicly available tools (LIANA, CellChat, CellPhoneDB and cell2cell).
